Description:
============
This is the reimplementation of Stratum protocol for server side from https://github.com/slush0/stratum.
The implementation bases on python3+ implementation.

Installation
============

Requirements:
python 3+
linux-based system

Following instructions will work on Ubuntu & Debian*:

Startup
=======
Start server:
twistd -ny launcher.tac

Start server *without* lowlevel messages of Twisted:
twistd -ny launcher.tac -l log/twistd.log
